There are a number of projects under the PPP programme and formerly considered under the programme, that are being advanced as part of the City Council’s strategy for the regeneration of its apartment complexes.

Fatima Mansions PPP — Phase 2 to be completed by October 2009;

Project proposals for the redevelopment of St. Michael’s Estate (former PPP project) are being considered by the Department for commencement in 2009;

Proposals for the former PPP projects at O’Devaney Gardens and Dominick Street are being prepared by the City Council for inclusion in their social housing construction programme;

Range of PPP projects including those at Croke Villas, Mountainview Court, St. Theresa’s Gardens, Charlemont Street and Bridgefoot Street;.
